4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive 16-week AI and Machine Learning Engineer bootcamp designed for beginners without prior experience in data science. The course includes Python, SQL, Streamlit, and statistics, enabling participants to build and deploy ML models. Students will work with algorithms for both supervised and unsupervised learning, while collaborating in small class sizes of 12. The program emphasizes real-world applications and the complete lifecycle of AI projects. Graduates receive certificates recognized by various organizations. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop